HEADWORD: Uranoso-
<hw>U`ra*no"so-</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
<def>A combining form (also used adjectively) from <ets>uranium</ets>;
-- used in naming certain complex compounds; <as>as in
<ex>uranoso</ex>-uranic oxide, <ex>uranoso</ex>-uranic
sulphate</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
